<L>__{exterior road with campsite. the same evening.}
<A>__{c.w. is driving down the road, hell for leather. nearing a campsite, where there are about six okie cars and pick up trucks all loaded down, with a number of poor families seated around a campfire, cooking. c.w. jams on the brakes. he gets out, looking totally exhausted. reaction shot. the faces of the okies, looking at this sudden presence in their midst. back to c.w.}
